Interface IEventDispatcher

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.EventListener, java.awt.event.KeyListener, java.awt.event.MouseListener, java.awt.event.MouseMotionListener, java.awt.event.MouseWheelListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Display

    public interface IEventDispatcher
extends java.awt.event.MouseMotionListener, java.awt.event.MouseWheelListener, java.awt.event.MouseListener, java.awt.event.KeyListener
    This interface dispatches all the input events (mouse events, keyboard events)
    to an action that are implemented from IAction by users.
    Since:
    V1.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Nan Cao
